&lt;li&gt;Experiment with AI-powered content creation: reels, short films, storytelling formats, and community-driven content&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as a brand ambassador – actively engaging with architects, engineers, contractors, and others in the industry&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and nurture relationships and communities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help lead and evolve MeltPlan’s narrative as a category-defining company&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay close to people: Conversations, DMs, comments, and industry discourse&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work directly on brand storytelling, creative direction, and growth initiatives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
